---
import '../styles/global.css'
import Header from "../components/Header.astro"
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Las Mejores Playas para el Verano</title>
</head>
<body>
    <Header/>
    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Las Mejores Playas para el Verano</h1>
            <p>Explora las playas más impresionantes para disfrutar del sol y la arena este verano.</p>
            <a href="/" class="cta-button">Descubrir Playas</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container main-content">
        <section id="beaches">
            <h2>Playas Destacadas</h2>
            <ul class="beaches">
                <li class="beach-item">
                    <img src="beach1.jpg" alt="Playa 1">
                    <div class="beach-info">
                        <h3>Playa del Sol</h3>
                        <p>Una playa con aguas cristalinas y arenas doradas, ideal para relajarse y disfrutar del sol.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="beach-item">
                    <img src="beach2.jpg" alt="Playa 2">
                    <div class="beach-info">
                        <h3>Playa Paraíso</h3>
                        <p>Con sus aguas turquesas y paisajes impresionantes, Playa Paraíso es un destino imperdible.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="beach-item">
                    <img src="beach3.jpg" alt="Playa 3">
                    <div class="beach-info">
                        <h3>Playa Tropical</h3>
                        <p>Un lugar perfecto para practicar deportes acuáticos y disfrutar de un ambiente vibrante.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <!-- Agrega más playas según sea necesario -->
            </ul>
        </section>
    </div>

    <Footer/>
</body>
</html>
<style>
    /* Reset básico */
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }

    .container {
        width: 80%;
        margin: auto;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* Estilos del hero */
    .hero-section {
        position: relative;
        height: 60vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: url('paris.jpg') no-repeat center center/cover;
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 0;
        max-width: 700px;
        padding: 0 20px;
        text-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .hero-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero-content p {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .cta-button {
        background-color: #ff5733;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #ff9a3c;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* Estilos del contenido principal */
    .main-content {
        padding: 2rem 0;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .main-content h2 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #ff5733;
    }

    .beaches {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .beach-item {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
        flex: 1 1 calc(33.333% - 1rem);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .beach-item:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    .beach-item img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        object-fit: cover;
    }

    .beach-info {
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .beach-info h3 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #ff5733;
    }

    .beach-info p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #666;
    }


    /* Estilos responsivos */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
            width: 90%;
        }

        .header-content {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        nav ul {
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-left: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .hero-section {
            height: 50vh;
        }

        .cta-button {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .beach-item {
            flex: 1 1 100%;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .cta-button {
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .hero-section {
            height: 60vh;
        }
    }
</style>